    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/bdc92024e6d9a178f499c2bb47f2fadd.avif?t=1751250189\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有独特的技能与属性，可根据战斗的需要进行合理搭配！无你是选择强大的近战战士、还是擅长施法的法师，都能找到适合自己的位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/eae6d1970c2523bf2ec218839f527e52.poster.avif?t=1751250189\" width=792 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/eae6d1970c2523bf2ec218839f527e52.webm?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/eae6d1970c2523bf2ec218839f527e52.mp4?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/a88784cca406ae631f697a3c8f0b403e.avif?t=1751250189\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择集结成圆，增强攻击，或是一字排开，提高速度。通过简单的切换操作，方便在瞬息万变的战斗中做出迅速反应，充分发挥团队的潜力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/3f17829d1d9af9c2154bb4637fe972de.poster.avif?t=1751250189\" width=792 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/3f17829d1d9af9c2154bb4637fe972de.webm?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/3f17829d1d9af9c2154bb4637fe972de.mp4?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/338e6e14d592189eec3c188b3a351aff.avif?t=1751250189\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的流派间相辅相成，可以构筑出丰富的战斗策略。探索各种可能性，发现隐藏的组合和最佳搭配，令你的勇士们在战斗中展现出非凡的力量与风格！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/776145ab61053a1da16fe47becad2e60.poster.avif?t=1751250189\" width=790 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/776145ab61053a1da16fe47becad2e60.webm?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/776145ab61053a1da16fe47becad2e60.mp4?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/f75829b1c04c89d6a896b36f29b4e3ea.avif?t=1751250189\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速且富有节奏感的打击体验，让每一次攻击都充满冲击力。伴随着流畅的动作和华丽的技能特效，带来令人上瘾的快节奏战斗体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/930e69e398e03372c6310661bbfad79b.poster.avif?t=1751250189\" width=790 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/930e69e398e03372c6310661bbfad79b.webm?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/930e69e398e03372c6310661bbfad79b.mp4?t=1751250189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
